room_title: Escape room "Detective Lockwood" by Riddler's Escape in St. Cloud
room_address: 510 25th Ave N, Suite 8 St Cloud, MN 56303
room_description: Eight crime scenes all over town revealed a suspicious gas substance that caused horrible side effects in all victims. The killer, known as the Green Reaper, is planning another attack and has kidnapped head detective on the case, Vincent Lockwood. You've been called in to gather evidence, find the Reaper's secret lair and uncover the mystery before more innocent people are hurt.
